            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間20日09:57，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>下跌79.76點（或1.01%），暫報7783.54點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+2.88%</li><li>近 1 月：-3.79%</li><li>近 3 月：+11.25%</li><li>近 6 月：+26.17%</li><li>今年以來：+11.01%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>成分股以連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)領跌。連貫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:COHR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/COHR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">COHR-US</a>)下跌5.21%；泰瑞達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TER:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TER\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TER-US</a>)下跌3.15%；安可(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AMKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AMKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AMKR-US</a>)下跌2.36%；Onto Innovation Inc.(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ONTO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ONTO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ONTO-US</a>)下跌2.24%；科磊(<a data-ga-click-